title: Were You Ever Shamed For Your Cultural Cuisine? Producer Romeo Was!
description:
Immigrants sound off! Were you ever shamed for the cultural cuisine you had in your lunchbox? 
Producer Romeo was transported right back to High School after a conversation with his niece.
